subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Venus, seeded 18th, went first, beating fellow American Lauren Davis, 6-2, 6-3. Serena, the top seed, went next, beating Vera Zvonareva of Russia, 7-5, 6-0.
